<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>账户状态变更通知 - SSL Online Judge</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header.active {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #28a745;
        }
        .header.banned {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dc3545;
        }
        .header.suspended {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .logo.active {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .logo.banned {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .logo.suspended {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .title.active {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .title.banned {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .title.suspended {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .status-box {
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .status-box.active {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
        }
        .status-box.banned {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        }
        .status-box.suspended {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .status-badge.active {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
        }
        .status-badge.banned {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }
        .status-badge.suspended {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #212529;
        }
        .reason-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #6c757d;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }
        .reason-box.active {
            border-left-color: #28a745;
        }
        .reason-box.banned {
            border-left-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .reason-box.suspended {
            border-left-color: #ffc107;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">
            <div class="logo {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">SSL Online Judge</div>
            <div>账户状态管理</div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="title {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">
            {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}
                ✅ 账户已激活
            {{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}
                🚫 账户已封禁
            {{else}}
                ⏸️ 账户已暂停
            {{/if}}
        </h2>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>您好 <strong>{{username}}</strong>，</p>
            
            <p>我们向您发送此邮件是为了通知您，您的SSL Online Judge账户状态已发生变更。</p>
            
            <div class="status-box {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">
                <h3>
                    {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}
                        🎉 账户状态更新
                    {{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}
                        ⚠️ 账户状态更新
                    {{else}}
                        📋 账户状态更新
                    {{/if}}
                </h3>
                <div class="status-badge {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">
                    {{newStatus}}
                </div>
                
                {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}
                    <p style="color: #28a745; font-weight: bold;">您的账户现在已完全激活，可以正常使用所有功能！</p>
                {{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}
                    <p style="color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold;">您的账户已被封禁，无法访问平台功能。</p>
                {{else}}
                    <p style="color: #856404; font-weight: bold;">您的账户已被暂停，部分功能可能受限。</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>用户名</th>
                    <td>{{username}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>新状态</th>
                    <td><strong>{{newStatus}}</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>变更时间</th>
                    <td>{{changeTime}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{#if reason}}
                <tr>
                    <th>变更原因</th>
                    <td>{{reason}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
            </table>
            
            {{#if reason}}
                <div class="reason-box {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}active{{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}banned{{else}}suspended{{/if}}">
                    <h4>📝 变更原因：</h4>
                    <p>{{reason}}</p>
                </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if (eq newStatus '已激活')}}
                <div class="info-box">
                    <h4>🎊 欢迎回来！</h4>
                    <p>您的账户已成功激活，现在可以：</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>正常登录和使用所有平台功能</li>
                        <li>提交代码和参与编程练习</li>
                        <li>参加编程竞赛和活动</li>
                        <li>访问学习资源和题库</li>
                        <li>与其他用户交流和讨论</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>感谢您继续使用SSL Online Judge！</p>
                </div>
            {{else if (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <h4>🚨 账户封禁说明</h4>
                    <p>您的账户已被封禁，这意味着：</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>无法登录SSL Online Judge平台</li>
                        <li>无法提交代码或参与竞赛</li>
                        <li>无法访问平台的任何功能</li>
                        <li>所有相关服务将被暂停</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>如果您认为这是误操作，请立即联系我们的技术支持团队。</strong></p>
                </div>
            {{else}}
                <div class="warning-box">
                    <h4>⏸️ 账户暂停说明</h4>
                    <p>您的账户已被暂停，这可能影响：</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>部分平台功能可能受限</li>
                        <li>代码提交可能被限制</li>
                        <li>竞赛参与可能受影响</li>
                        <li>某些资源访问可能被限制</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>请联系管理员了解具体限制和恢复条件。</strong></p>
                </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>📞 需要帮助？</h4>
                <p>如果您对账户状态变更有任何疑问，或需要申诉，请联系我们：</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li><strong>技术支持邮箱：</strong> <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></li>
                    <li><strong>管理员邮箱：</strong> admin@ssloj.com</li>
                    <li><strong>申诉渠道：</strong> appeal@ssloj.com</li>
                </ul>
                <p>我们会在收到您的邮件后24小时内回复。</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#unless (eq newStatus '已封禁')}}
                <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <h4>💡 温馨提示：</h4>
                    <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                        <li>请遵守平台使用规则和社区准则</li>
                        <li>保护好您的账户信息，不要与他人分享</li>
                        <li>如发现异常活动，请及时联系我们</li>
                        <li>定期查看平台公告和更新信息</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            {{/unless}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>此邮件由SSL Online Judge系统自动发送，请勿回复。</p>
            <p>我们致力于为所有用户提供安全、公平的学习环境。</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 SSL Online Judge. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>